Detailed Description

cvmx_stx::_spi4_stat

STX_SPI4_STAT - Spi4 status channel control register

Notes: Restrictions: Both the calendar table and the LEN and M parameters must be completely setup before writing the Interface enable (INF_EN) and Status channel enabled (ST_EN) asserted.

The calendar table will only be enabled when LEN > 0.

Current rev will only support LVTTL status IO.
